  "description": "Use when configuring or troubleshooting a Salesforce B2C Commerce (SFCC) storefront \u2014 including Business Manager site creation, SFRA cartridge path setup, customer groups, search index rebuilding, and key quota limits. Trigger keywords: SFCC, Commerce Cloud, Business Manager, storefront, cartridge, SFRA, site preferences, replication. NOT for B2B Commerce on Lightning platform (WebStore, BuyerGroup, CommerceEntitlementPolicy \u2014 see admin/b2b-commerce-store-setup for that).",
